    <string name="help_text">
        Welcome to the Meal Planner app!\n\nIn the first tab of the navigation menu, you can
        add dishes that you frequently prepare.
        For example, you already have access to 12 dishes. You can delete them by long-pressing.\n\nOn
        the other tabs, breakfast, lunch, and dinner are randomly generated based on the settings
        from the above-mentioned list of dishes.\n\nIn the settings, located in the top right corner of the screen,
        you can specify the daily calorie range and the percentage distribution of meals.\n\nEnjoy your meal!
    </string>

